er: "Dukhesva Anudhvigna-manah Sukhesu-Vigatasprhah Vita-Raga-Bhaya-Krodhah=
 Sthita-Dhira Munir Uchyate" Gita 2:56 [Miseries do not agitate the mind, i=
n sukha (fleeting happiness) there is no elation, such a one who is free fr=
om attachment, fear and anger, is a sage of steady mind.]

Tough? Sure. But=
 no harm in making an effort. This is something to be tried on a regular ba=
sis, day in and day out.

